# Axodus Blocker Register

Last reviewed: 2026-06-30

## AXODUS-PORTFOLIO-REQ-01 Preserved Global Gates

Academy, Mining and Defi closures resolve bounded non-production maturity cycles only. ACS remains paused and Marketplace remains backlog-ready.

| Nucleus | Current blocker posture |
|---|---|
| ACS | Execution, provisioning, credentials, signing, providers, runtime mutation and L4 Consolidated gates remain blocked; `ACS-GOV-03` deferred and `ACS-GOV-04` not opened. |
| Academy | Real rewards, certification/verification, on-chain issuance, treasury, signing, payment, billing, payouts, settlement, providers, production APIs/databases, minting and contract writes remain blocked. |
| Mining | Real mining/hashrate, provider execution, custody, treasury, signing, payouts/yield, billing, settlement, equipment/capital execution, contracts, issuance, production APIs/databases/providers and legal classification remain blocked. |
| Defi | All 16 blockers remain open; treasury execution, custody, signing, financial/provider execution, contract writes, real yield, production surfaces, regulated readiness and investment recommendation remain blocked; `ADMIN_MUTATION` remains `UNSAFE`. |
| Marketplace | Payment, settlement, treasury, wallet, minting and production commerce remain blocked; Phase 12A is not activated. |
| Trading | Live trading, credentials, withdrawals, production database, signing, treasury and financial execution remain blocked. |
| Lottery | Randomness, prizes, payouts, compliance, treasury, settlement and contracts remain blocked. |
| Documentation | Publication authority and root/global versioning remain unresolved; publication execution is not authorized. |

Global closed-gate set: production, treasury execution, custody, wallet/signing, financial execution, provider execution, contract writes, real yield, settlement, payouts, billing execution, real credentials, production APIs, production databases, regulated product readiness and investment recommendation.

